<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Car Service Appointment Confirmation</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Car Service Appointment Confirmation</h1>
    <p>Hello <%= customerName %>,</p>
    <p>
      Your appointment for car service has been confirmed. Below are the
      details:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Vehicle Number:</strong> <%= vehicleNumber %></li>
      <li><strong>Date:</strong> <%= appointmentDate %></li>
      <li><strong>Time:</strong> <%= appointmentTime %></li>
      <li><strong>Service Type:</strong> <%= serviceType %></li>
      <li><strong>Car Model:</strong> <%= carModel %></li>
      <% if(additionalNotes !== ""){ %>
      <li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> <%= additionalNotes %></li>
      <% } %>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Thank you for choosing our service. If you have any questions or need to
      reschedule, please contact us.
    </p>
    <p>Best regards,<br />Car Service Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
